## Objective
Integrate the new `totemParser` service into the API endpoints to return fully parsed project and sprint payloads.

## Requirements
- Update GET `/api/instances` in `server/src/index.ts` to return fully parsed project objects including configuration from `project.config.yml` and the standard README.
- Add GET `/api/instances/:id/sprints` endpoint to fetch detailed sprint history for a specific instance.
- The endpoints should return JSON matching the extended shared types.
